title: Inter Workflow Real-Time Forwarding Agent Events - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: Agent Message Events An information message from the agent, stated according to the configuration done in the Event Notification Editor. For further information about the agent message event type, see Agent Event . Inserted batch: filename Reported when a file has been closed in the target directory (hence ready for collection). The message is only used in batch workflows. Debug Events There are no debug events for this agent. Loading
